topic.title: Forum Info
topic.body:
Forum Rules:
Please be kind and courteous to each other
More rules will be added as things goes by
How to post/gain access:
select login in 
you will get a prompt register an ID with any of these sites
create an account there
go back here and select login as with the said new made account
